<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">

    <h1>Dante Rossetti</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                  ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Aenean vel elit scelerisque mauris pellentesque pulvinar pellentesque. 
          Ac tincidunt vitae semper quis lectus nulla at. Dui sapien eget mi proin 
          sed libero. Nisl vel pretium lectus quam id. Volutpat est velit egestas 
          dui id ornare. Nibh sit amet commodo nulla. Lorem donec massa sapien 
          faucibus et molestie ac feugiat. Vitae congue eu consequat ac felis. 
          Iaculis at erat pellentesque adipiscing commodo elit at imperdiet. 
          Ultrices dui sapien eget mi proin sed. Nullam ac tortor vitae purus 
          faucibus ornare suspendisse. Nascetur ridiculus mus mauris vitae 
          ultricies leo integer. Commodo elit at imperdiet dui. Suscipit 
          adipiscing bibendum est ultricies integer quis auctor elit sed. 
          Vivamus at augue eget arcu. Vulputate eu scelerisque felis 
          imperdiet proin fermentum leo. Ut lectus arcu bibendum at. Vitae 
          nunc sed velit dignissim sodales ut eu sem. At erat pellentesque 
          adipiscing commodo elit at imperdiet dui.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
            >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
            >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
